377
00:23:35,430 --> 00:23:36,870
Shibata?

378
00:23:36,870 --> 00:23:38,390
Ten Shibata?

379
00:23:38,390 --> 00:23:42,230
Stane sa z neho kúzelná bábika menom Nitai.

380
00:23:42,230 --> 00:23:45,230
Prajem si, aby som toho mohol urobiť viac.

381
00:23:45,230 --> 00:23:46,760
Mrzí ma to, Tanuma.

382
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:48,030
Natsume!

